# 🎮 Super Mario JS  

A **Super Mario Bros–style 2D platformer** built using **JavaScript, HTML5, and Phaser.js**.  
Play it directly in your browser — no downloads, no installs, just pure retro fun! 🚀  

---

## ✨ Features
- 🏃‍♂️ Smooth player movement & jumping  
- 🌍 Gravity & collision physics  
- 🟩 Platforms, obstacles & hazards  
- 👾 Enemies to avoid or defeat  
- 💰 Coins & collectibles  
- 🎵 Retro-inspired visuals & sounds  
- 🖥️ Playable in any modern desktop browser  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- 🎨 **HTML5 Canvas / Phaser.js** – rendering & engine  
- ⚡ **JavaScript (ES6)** – game logic & interactivity  
- 🎭 **CSS3** – layout & styling  

